{"tid":446261,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"次貨 Pixel 2 照入盒  代工商玩謝 Google","createTime":"2017-10-24T06:53:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-25T17:58:48.000Z","uid":23677,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"acbe7d346ac93d5de5e95afdb565edcdc578930e","tid":446261,"uid":23677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T06:53:06.000Z","msg":"打開新買手機包裝的興奮感覺，相信不少人都試過，如果開機後發現手機有問題，應該會非常失望。不過 Reddit 討論區一位消費者，他的失望指數比任何人都要高，因為他一打開剛剛入手的 Pixel 2 包裝後，還未開機就已經知道自己手上的新機屬於次貨。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這名不幸的消費者，日前收到他訂購的 Quite Black 黑色機身 128GB Pixel 2，當他興奮地開箱時，卻發現機身跟隨著一塊罕見的藍色紙條。這張紙條相信是代工生產商的質量控制人員，在檢測手機後留低，表示手機的機身出現外觀損壞。附有這張紙條的手機，一般都不會裝箱出廠，至於為什麼會這麼大意，相信只有為 Google 代工生產 Pixel 2 的廠商才知道。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n收到這樣一部次貨，這名消費者當然非常失望，而他亦即時聯絡 Google，幸好 Google 亦表示會即時處理。Google 今次發表 Pixel 2 和 Pixel 2 XL 並非一帆風順，最近就傳出因為供不應求，部份訂單需要延期 1 個月交付，為了賠償顧客的損失，Google 要送出保護殼補鑊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4541/209352/1/1/135732/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4541%2F209352%2F1%2F1%2F135732%2F&d=TeY7SAw3qJ28urUpDWKnML%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=a5d09089\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4541/209352/1/1/135732/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3ef64ac710fe412c446104f233689eaad1f8979","tid":446261,"uid":23677,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T06:54:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/24/145425_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F24%2F145425_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=43b34056&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bcd305df6decdda8a9f372d15e323511b2602be1","tid":446261,"uid":14476,"like":32,"dislike